{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "SAMtools 189 (v1.9-93-g0ca96a4) was used for sorting and indexing the alignments.",
    "Read counts (mapping quality [MQ] ≥ 0) per 10-kb bin (nonoverlapping) for all samples were calculated with multiBamSummary from deepTools 195 (v3.3.0).",
    "Read counts were normalized by the total number of counts in the chromosomes per sample (Supplementary Note 5).",
    "Peaks were called with MACS2 196 (v2.2.7.1) and custom scripts (https://bitbucket.org/rokhsar- lab/xentr10/src/master/chipseq).",
    "The reads from the F 2 mapping population 25 were aligned to the v10 genome sequence using BWA-MEM 188 (v0.7.17-r1188)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
